        "It has area of 1180 sqft and is available at a rent of Rs. 19,000. This residential property is ready-to-move-in. It is made in way to provide a comfortable living for the residents. The site is in close proximity to various civic utilities. Contact us for more details. ",
        "Well designed 2 bhk multistorey apartment is available at a prime location in Shivshakti Developers Mumbai Shiv Ornate. It has a built-up area of 1120 sqft and is available for rent at Rs. 12,500 per month . The house is unfurnished. It is a ready-to-move-in property. It is made in way to provide a comfortable living for the residents. ",
