        "It has a built-up area of 750 sqft and is available for rent at Rs. 28,500 per month . The house is unfurnished. It is a 10 year old ready-to-move-in property. The time you'll spend here will become the greatest moment of your life that will also help you to relieve, relax & evoke a great sense of happiness. Kindly call us for details. ",
        "The house is semi-furnished. It has power backup. Other amenities include children's play area, intercom, lift available, gymnasium and club house. It is east facing property. It is a ready-to-move-in property. If you are interested, please contact us for more details. "
